  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 18th level, your sight can be shared even beyond death. When you fail your third death saving throw, or would be killed outright, you momentarily wake from the unconscious condition and can choose a creature you can see.</p><p>You send that creature your memories, any piece of information you know. That creature also gains up to two Ouyoku clan Hijutsu that you know of B-Rank or lower. Once you use this feature, you cannot do so again.</p>",
